app-store-connect-mcp

Tool definitions in src/generated/ are produced by scripts/generate.ts from
Apple Inc.'s published App Store Connect OpenAPI specification (spec/openapi.json).
That specification is Apple's factual description of its own public API, and is
redistributed here so the generator is reproducible without network access.

